{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "28.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "凡出言談、由文學之為道也，則不可而不先立義法。", "text_normalized": "凡出言談、由文學之為道也，則不可而不先立義法。", "canonical_ref": "28.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "若言而無義，譬猶立朝夕於員鈞之上也，則雖有巧工，必不能得正焉。", "text_normalized": "若言而無義，譬猶立朝夕於員鈞之上也，則雖有巧工，必不能得正焉。", "canonical_ref": "28.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "然今天下之情偽，未可得而識也。", "text_normalized": "然今天下之情偽，未可得而識也。", "canonical_ref": "28.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "故使言有三法。", "text_normalized": "故使言有三法。", "canonical_ref": "28.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "三法者何也？", "text_normalized": "三法者何也？", "canonical_ref": "28.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "有本之者，有原之者，有用之者。", "text_normalized": "有本之者，有原之者，有用之者。", "canonical_ref": "28.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "於其本之也，考之天鬼之志，聖王之事。", "text_normalized": "於其本之也，考之天鬼之志，聖王之事。", "canonical_ref": "28.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "於其原之也，征以先王之書。", "text_normalized": "於其原之也，征以先王之書。", "canonical_ref": "28.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "用之奈何？", "text_normalized": "用之奈何？", "canonical_ref": "28.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "發而為刑。", "text_normalized": "發而為刑。", "canonical_ref": "28.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "此言之三法也。", "text_normalized": "此言之三法也。", "canonical_ref": "28.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "今天下之士君子，或以命為亡。", "text_normalized": "今天下之士君子，或以命為亡。", "canonical_ref": "28.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "我所以知命之有與亡者，以眾人耳目之情，知有與亡。", "text_normalized": "我所以知命之有與亡者，以眾人耳目之情，知有與亡。", "canonical_ref": "28.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "有聞之，有見之，謂之有。", "text_normalized": "有聞之，有見之，謂之有。", "canonical_ref": "28.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "莫之聞，莫之見，謂之亡。", "text_normalized": "莫之聞，莫之見，謂之亡。", "canonical_ref": "28.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "然胡不嘗考之百姓之情？", "text_normalized": "然胡不嘗考之百姓之情？", "canonical_ref": "28.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "自古以及今，生民以來者，亦嘗見命之物、聞命之聲者乎？", "text_normalized": "自古以及今，生民以來者，亦嘗見命之物、聞命之聲者乎？", "canonical_ref": "28.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "則未嘗有也。", "text_normalized": "則未嘗有也。", "canonical_ref": "28.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "若以百姓為愚不肖，耳目之情，不足因而為法。", "text_normalized": "若以百姓為愚不肖，耳目之情，不足因而為法。", "canonical_ref": "28.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "然則胡不嘗考之諸侯之傳言流語乎？", "text_normalized": "然則胡不嘗考之諸侯之傳言流語乎？", "canonical_ref": "28.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "自古以及今，生民以來者，亦嘗有聞命之聲、見命之體者乎？", "text_normalized": "自古以及今，生民以來者，亦嘗有聞命之聲、見命之體者乎？", "canonical_ref": "28.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "則未嘗有也。", "text_normalized": "則未嘗有也。", "canonical_ref": "28.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "然胡不嘗考之聖王之事？", "text_normalized": "然胡不嘗考之聖王之事？", "canonical_ref": "28.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "古之聖王，舉孝子而勸之事親，尊賢良而勸之為善，發憲布令以教誨，明賞罰以勸沮。", "text_normalized": "古之聖王，舉孝子而勸之事親，尊賢良而勸之為善，發憲布令以教誨，明賞罰以勸沮。", "canonical_ref": "28.25", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 26, "text_original": "若此，則亂者可使治，而危者可使安矣。", "text_normalized": "若此，則亂者可使治，而危者可使安矣。", "canonical_ref": "28.26", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 27, "text_original": "若以為不然，昔者桀之所亂，湯治之。", "text_normalized": "若以為不然，昔者桀之所亂，湯治之。", "canonical_ref": "28.27", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 28, "text_original": "紂之所亂，武王治之。", "text_normalized": "紂之所亂，武王治之。", "canonical_ref": "28.28", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 29, "text_original": "此世不渝而民不改，上變政而民易教，其在湯、武則治，其在桀、紂則亂。", "text_normalized": "此世不渝而民不改，上變政而民易教，其在湯、武則治，其在桀、紂則亂。", "canonical_ref": "28.29", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 30, "text_original": "安危治亂，在上之發政也，則豈可謂有命哉！", "text_normalized": "安危治亂，在上之發政也，則豈可謂有命哉！", "canonical_ref": "28.30", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 31, "text_original": "夫曰有命云者，亦不然矣。", "text_normalized": "夫曰有命云者，亦不然矣。", "canonical_ref": "28.31", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 32, "text_original": "今夫有命者言曰：", "text_normalized": "今夫有命者言曰：", "canonical_ref": "28.32", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 33, "text_original": "我非作之後世也，自昔三代有若言以傳流矣，今故先生對之？", "text_normalized": "我非作之後世也，自昔三代有若言以傳流矣，今故先生對之？", "canonical_ref": "28.33", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 34, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "28.34", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 35, "text_original": "夫有命者，不志昔也三代之聖、善人與？", "text_normalized": "夫有命者，不志昔也三代之聖、善人與？", "canonical_ref": "28.35", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 36, "text_original": "意亡昔三代之暴、不肖人也？", "text_normalized": "意亡昔三代之暴、不肖人也？", "canonical_ref": "28.36", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 37, "text_original": "何以知之？", "text_normalized": "何以知之？", "canonical_ref": "28.37", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 38, "text_original": "初之列士桀大夫，慎言知行，此上有以規諫其君長，下有以教順其百姓。", "text_normalized": "初之列士桀大夫，慎言知行，此上有以規諫其君長，下有以教順其百姓。", "canonical_ref": "28.38", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 39, "text_original": "故上得其君長之賞，下得其百姓之譽。", "text_normalized": "故上得其君長之賞，下得其百姓之譽。", "canonical_ref": "28.39", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0040", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 40, "text_original": "列士桀大夫聲聞不廢，流傳至今，而天下皆曰其力也，必不能曰我見命焉。", "text_normalized": "列士桀大夫聲聞不廢，流傳至今，而天下皆曰其力也，必不能曰我見命焉。", "canonical_ref": "28.40", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 41, "text_original": "是故昔者三代之暴王，不繆其耳目之淫，不慎其心志之辟，外之馳騁田獵畢弋，內沉於酒樂，而不顧其國家百姓之政，繁為無用，暴逆百姓，使下不親其上，是故國為虛厲，身在刑僇之中，不肯曰：", "text_normalized": "是故昔者三代之暴王，不繆其耳目之淫，不慎其心志之辟，外之馳騁田獵畢弋，內沉於酒樂，而不顧其國家百姓之政，繁為無用，暴逆百姓，使下不親其上，是故國為虛厲，身在刑僇之中，不肯曰：", "canonical_ref": "28.41", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0042", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 42, "text_original": "我罷不肖，我為刑政不善。", "text_normalized": "我罷不肖，我為刑政不善。", "canonical_ref": "28.42", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0043", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 43, "text_original": "必曰：", "text_normalized": "必曰：", "canonical_ref": "28.43", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0044", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 44, "text_original": "我命故且亡。", "text_normalized": "我命故且亡。", "canonical_ref": "28.44", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0045", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 45, "text_original": "雖昔也三代之窮民，亦由此也。", "text_normalized": "雖昔也三代之窮民，亦由此也。", "canonical_ref": "28.45", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0046", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 46, "text_original": "內之不能善事其親戚，外不能善事其君長，惡恭儉而好簡易，貪飲食而惰從事，衣食之財不足，使身至有饑寒凍餒之憂，必不能曰：", "text_normalized": "內之不能善事其親戚，外不能善事其君長，惡恭儉而好簡易，貪飲食而惰從事，衣食之財不足，使身至有饑寒凍餒之憂，必不能曰：", "canonical_ref": "28.46", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0047", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 47, "text_original": "我罷不肖，我從事不疾。", "text_normalized": "我罷不肖，我從事不疾。", "canonical_ref": "28.47", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0048", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 48, "text_original": "必曰：", "text_normalized": "必曰：", "canonical_ref": "28.48", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0049", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 49, "text_original": "我命固且窮。", "text_normalized": "我命固且窮。", "canonical_ref": "28.49", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0050", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 50, "text_original": "雖昔也三代之偽民，亦猶此也。", "text_normalized": "雖昔也三代之偽民，亦猶此也。", "canonical_ref": "28.50", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0051", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 51, "text_original": "繁飾有命，以教眾愚樸人久矣。", "text_normalized": "繁飾有命，以教眾愚樸人久矣。", "canonical_ref": "28.51", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0052", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 52, "text_original": "聖王之患此也，故書之竹帛，琢之金石。", "text_normalized": "聖王之患此也，故書之竹帛，琢之金石。", "canonical_ref": "28.52", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0053", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 53, "text_original": "於先王之書《仲虺之告》曰：", "text_normalized": "於先王之書《仲虺之告》曰：", "canonical_ref": "28.53", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0054", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 54, "text_original": "「我聞有夏人矯天命，布命於下，帝式是惡，用厥師。", "text_normalized": "「我聞有夏人矯天命，布命於下，帝式是惡，用厥師。", "canonical_ref": "28.54", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0055", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 55, "text_original": "」此語夏王桀之執有命也，湯與仲虺共非之。", "text_normalized": "」此語夏王桀之執有命也，湯與仲虺共非之。", "canonical_ref": "28.55", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0056", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 56, "text_original": "先王之書《太誓》之言然，曰：", "text_normalized": "先王之書《太誓》之言然，曰：", "canonical_ref": "28.56", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0057", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 57, "text_original": "「紂夷之居，而不肯事上帝，棄闕其先神而不祀也，曰：", "text_normalized": "「紂夷之居，而不肯事上帝，棄闕其先神而不祀也，曰：", "canonical_ref": "28.57", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0058", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 58, "text_original": "『我民有命，毋僇其務。", "text_normalized": "『我民有命，毋僇其務。", "canonical_ref": "28.58", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0059", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 59, "text_original": "』天不亦棄縱而不葆。", "text_normalized": "』天不亦棄縱而不葆。", "canonical_ref": "28.59", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0060", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 60, "text_original": "」此言紂之執有命也，武王以《太誓》非之。", "text_normalized": "」此言紂之執有命也，武王以《太誓》非之。", "canonical_ref": "28.60", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0061", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 61, "text_original": "有於《三代》、《不國》有之，曰：", "text_normalized": "有於《三代》、《不國》有之，曰：", "canonical_ref": "28.61", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0062", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 62, "text_original": "「女毋崇天之有命也。", "text_normalized": "「女毋崇天之有命也。", "canonical_ref": "28.62", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0063", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 63, "text_original": "」命《三》、《不國》亦言命之無也。", "text_normalized": "」命《三》、《不國》亦言命之無也。", "canonical_ref": "28.63", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0064", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 64, "text_original": "於召公之執令於然，曰：", "text_normalized": "於召公之執令於然，曰：", "canonical_ref": "28.64", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0065", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 65, "text_original": "「敬哉！", "text_normalized": "「敬哉！", "canonical_ref": "28.65", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0066", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 66, "text_original": "無天命。", "text_normalized": "無天命。", "canonical_ref": "28.66", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0067", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 67, "text_original": "惟予仁人，而無造言，不自降天之哉得之。", "text_normalized": "惟予仁人，而無造言，不自降天之哉得之。", "canonical_ref": "28.67", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0068", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 68, "text_original": "」在於商、夏之詩書曰：", "text_normalized": "」在於商、夏之詩書曰：", "canonical_ref": "28.68", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0069", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 69, "text_original": "命者，暴王作之。", "text_normalized": "命者，暴王作之。", "canonical_ref": "28.69", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0070", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 70, "text_original": "且今天下之士君子，將欲辯是非利害之故，當天有命者，不可不疾非也。", "text_normalized": "且今天下之士君子，將欲辯是非利害之故，當天有命者，不可不疾非也。", "canonical_ref": "28.70", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0071", "section_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii", "source_id": "mozi-028-anti-fatalism-ii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 71, "text_original": "執有命者，此天下之厚害也，是故子墨子非也。", "text_normalized": "執有命者，此天下之厚害也，是故子墨子非也。", "canonical_ref": "28.71", "notes": ""}
